### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@userId  = PASTE_USER_ID_FROM_SEED_OUTPUT

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Place a valid bet ($100)
POST {{baseUrl}}/place-bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "amount": 100
}

### Place the same bet again — should fail with "Insufficient balance"
POST {{baseUrl}}/place-bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "amount": 100
}

### Invalid userId — should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/place-bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "not-a-real-id",
  "amount": 10
}

### Zero / negative amount — should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/place-bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "amount": 0
}

### Unknown user — should return 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/place-bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "64b0000000000000000000aa",
  "amount": 10
}
